de Carnaval. Na segunda-feira, foi a vez do branco e azul dos Filhos de Gandhy, com seus atabaques, agog\\u00f4s e xequer\\u00eas, darem as boas-vindas aos passageiros. No \\u00faltimo dia de atra\\u00e7\\u00f5es no metr\\u00f4, na ter\\u00e7a-feira, a banda Mal\\u00ea DeBal\\u00ea levou alegria e ritmo para dentro da Esta\\u00e7\\u00e3o Lapa com sua dan\\u00e7a. \\u201cO opera\\u00e7\\u00e3o do metr\\u00f4 no Carnaval cumpriu com um dos objetivos da concession\\u00e1ria \\u2013 aproximar o metr\\u00f4 da sociedade soteropolitana\\u201d, afirmou o Gestor de Atendimento da CCR Metr\\u00f4 Bahia, Hamilton Trindade.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\\"><em><strong>Fonte: Secom Bahia<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/p>","fulltext":"","state":1,"catid":"8","created":"2015-02-21 07:51:41","created_by":"303","created_by_alias":"","modified":"2015-02-21 08:30:00","modified_by":"303","checked_out":"303","checked_out_time":"2015-02-21 08:29:50","publish_up":"2015-02-21 07:51:41","publish_down":"0000-00-00 00:00:00","images":"{\\"image_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"float_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_intro_caption\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"float_fulltext\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_alt\\":\\"\\",\\"image_fulltext_caption\\":\\"\\"}","urls":"{\\"urla\\":false,\\"urlatext\\":\\"\\",\\"targeta\\":\\"\\",\\"urlb\\":false,\\"urlbtext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetb\\":\\"\\",\\"urlc\\":false,\\"urlctext\\":\\"\\",\\"targetc\\":\\"\\"}","attribs":"{\\"show_title\\":\\"\\",\\"link_titles\\":\\"\\",\\"show_tags\\":\\"\\",\\"show_intro\\":\\"\\",\\"info_block_position\\":\\"\\",\\"show_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"link_parent_category\\":\\"\\",\\"show_author\\":\\"\\",\\"link_author\\":\\"\\",\\"show_create_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_modify_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_publish_date\\":\\"\\",\\"show_item_navigation\\":\\"\\",\\"show_icons\\":\\"\\",\\"show_print_icon\\":\\"\\",\\"show